snippet.title: PS4 | KAMEN RIDER Climax Fighters - 2nd Trailer
snippet.description: KAMEN RIDER Climax Fighters for the PlayStation®4 which will be released in Southeast Asia (Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, the Philippines and Indonesia) on 7th December 2017, in Japanese voiceover with English subtitles.
